Peripherals		Requirement			Pin Ref.	Assigned Pin
---			---				---		---
Button			1 GPIO input			ButtonIn	GPIO 4
Red LED			1 GPIO output			RedOut		GPIO 5
RGB LED			3 PWM channels (@ max)		R		PWM - GPIO 13	Dominant colour
							G		PWM - GPIO 12 	
							B		PWM - GPIO 14 	(Weakest Color - no PWM perhaps)
Motor			1 PWM channel (essential)	MotorIn		PWM - GPIO 15
Charging Indicator	1 GPIO input			V-USBin		ADC
Programmming/ Debug	1 USART peripheral (2)		Rx		URXD
							Tx		UTXD
External Memory		1 TWI peripheral (2)		SCL		GPIO0 / SCL
							SDA		GPIO2 / SDA
Extra			-				-		GPIO 16

Total:							10 (+1) pins

Notes:
All GPIO except GPIO16 are PWM channels
